text:
This study project will be developed studying 
-Danish and European historic documents and previous research about the Euro;
-old and contemporary Danish journalistic articles;
 -Danish and European Institutions such as ECB, European Commission, Danish Ministry of Economy and Foreign Affairs, and it will be necessary to make and analyse interviews to Danish and European politicians, economists and experts of this historic and economic field.

